## Directory Layout

- `wiki/` — LLM-maintained knowledge (entities, concepts, sources, comparisons)
- `raw/` — Immutable source documents
- `outputs/` — Generated deliverables
- `.forge/agents/` — Agent personas with SKILL.md and capabilities menus
- `.forge/skills/{phase}/` — Workflows organized by research lifecycle phase
- `.forge/config.yaml` — Runtime configuration
- `.forge/_config/` — Manifests (skill, agent, file catalogs)

