## Research Lifecycle

1. **Acquisition**: ingest-source, batch-ingest, web-research
2. **Compilation**: update-entities, update-concepts, cross-reference
3. **Analysis**: query-wiki, generate-comparison, adversarial-review
4. **Synthesis**: compile-output, generate-slides, export-report
5. **Maintenance**: lint-wiki, reindex, stats

## Conventions

- Citation format: {{config.wiki.citation_format}}
{{#if (eq config.wiki.cross_ref_style "wikilink")}}
- Internal links: `[[Page Name]]`
{{else}}
- Internal links: `[Page Name](./page-name.md)`
{{/if}}
- Page templates in `.forge/templates/`
- Runtime config in `.forge/config.yaml`
- Always update `wiki/index.md` and `wiki/log.md` after operations
- Never modify files in `raw/`

## Tools

- `./.forge/tools/search.sh "query"` — Full-text search
- `./.forge/tools/pdf-to-md.py <file.pdf>` — Convert PDF to markdown
- `./.forge/tools/transcribe.sh <file>` — Transcribe audio/video
{{#if (includes config.workflows.tools "qmd")}}
- `qmd search "query"` — Semantic search
{{/if}}
